[Student "S"]
{EAST thinks there might be slam if WEST holds both minor Aces, so he tries Blackwood.

When WEST shows just one Ace EAST is afraid he will have a trump loser as well, so 
he stops at 5\H.

It turns out that EAST might make twelve tricks, depending on the \HK situation.}

