[Student "S"]
{WEST responds 2NT, showing 8+ points with no 5-card suit. 

EAST only needs to know how many Aces are in the WEST hand. He must use Gerber since 
4NT in this situation would not be Blackwood. 

When WEST shows two Aces EAST bids 6NT.}

